{
  "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 41040,
      "text": "一间教室里坐着二十三个人，我问一句：有没有两个人生日恰好在同一天？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "大多数人会觉得，一年有三百六十五天，这么巧的事应该很少见。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "可数学给出的答案是：这件事发生的概率，竟然超过了一半。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "counter",
      "line_id": "cnt-1",
      "filename": "counter-cnt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/counter-cnt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "我们容易把问题想成：某个人和我同一天，那确实很难。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "counter",
      "line_id": "cnt-2",
      "filename": "counter-cnt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/counter-cnt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "但真正比较的是任意两个人的配对，二十三个人能凑出两百五十三对。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "counter",
      "line_id": "cnt-3",
      "filename": "counter-cnt-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/counter-cnt-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "这么多对同时去碰运气，撞上的机会自然就大了起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "complement",
      "line_id": "cmp-1",
      "filename": "complement-cmp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/complement-cmp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "直接数碰撞很麻烦，我们换个角度，先算所有人生日都不同的概率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "complement",
      "line_id": "cmp-2",
      "filename": "complement-cmp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/complement-cmp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "第二个人要避开一天，第三个避开两天，一路乘下去，这个乘积越来越小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "complement",
      "line_id": "cmp-3",
      "filename": "complement-cmp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/complement-cmp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "用一减去这个乘积，就是至少两人同天的概率了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "result",
      "line_id": "res-1",
      "filename": "result-res-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/result-res-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "算下来，二十三个人时概率约为百分之五十点七，刚好过半。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "result",
      "line_id": "res-2",
      "filename": "result-res-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/result-res-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "到了七十个人，概率高达百分之九十九点九，几乎必然会撞。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "拖动滑块改变人数，看曲线怎样迅速爬过那条百分之五十的虚线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 44064,
      "text": "再点模拟按钮,让计算机反复布置房间，模拟频率会紧紧贴着理论曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "生日悖论的关键，是比较所有配对，而不是拿自己去比。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "借助补事件，我们把复杂的概率算得干净利落。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "birthday-paradox",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/birthday-paradox/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "直觉常常骗人，而数学帮我们看清真相，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 35.489999999999995,
  "total_size": 567936
}